StepUp Backend
This is the backend service for the StepUp project. It is built using Django and provides APIs for managing test results.
Setup Instructions
Prerequisites
Python 3.8 or higher
MySQL database
pip (Python package installer)

#Installation
Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/ne-ha-bh/capdev_stepup.git
Create a virtual environment and activate it:

python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # On Windows, use `venv\Scripts\activate`
Install the required packages:

cd stepup
pip install -r requirements.txt
Configure the database connection in settings.py:


Running the Application
Start the Django application:
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py runserver
The application will be available at http://127.0.0.1:8000/

API Endpoints

Upload Data: POST /upload
User Details: GET /user-details
Candidates Pass: GET /in-progress-candidate
Candidates Fail: GET /fail-candidates
Candidates In Progress: GET /pass-candidates
Total Invites: GET /invited-candidates
Participant Details: GET /participant-details

